01:17:16.112 --> 01:17:19.592
a really striking effect, and you see this across histologies,

1326
01:17:19.652 --> 01:17:23.252
across different tumor derived cell lines.

1327
01:17:23.432 --> 01:17:26.632
So it's not just in one tumor context.

1328
01:17:27.412 --> 01:17:30.452
If you look at matched histology matched data,

1329
01:17:31.372 --> 01:17:35.032
this is the percentile sensitivity of

1330
01:17:35.412 --> 01:17:38.802
lung-- just a way to interpret this, lung cancer cells treated with

