01:17:46.132 --> 01:17:49.672
sensitivity if they are RB disrupted.

1334
01:17:49.792 --> 01:17:51.512
And this is multiple cell lines in each.

1335
01:17:51.652 --> 01:17:54.272
This is the median sensitivity, the median percentile.

