01:17:58.572 --> 01:18:02.452
increase in sensitivity in cells even matched to histology in

1338
01:18:02.492 --> 01:18:05.532
cells that have RB pathway inactivation.

1339
01:18:05.552 --> 01:18:08.802
And if you look at the RB1 gene directly, this becomes actually rather

1340
01:18:08.892 --> 01:18:12.824
striking.So this was really interesting because

