1440
01:24:11.804 --> 01:24:15.604
prognosis because it picks up the copy number high endometrial tumors

1441
01:24:15.644 --> 01:24:19.524
like serous and carcinosarcomas that usually have a worse prognosis than

1442
01:24:19.584 --> 01:24:23.384
other endometrioid histologies.So with that, I'm just going to thank

1443
01:24:23.764 --> 01:24:27.464
a lot of people who contributed to this work and happy to take any

1444
01:24:27.504 --> 01:24:30.004
questions. Thank you. Thank you all for your attention.

1445
01:24:38.784 --> 01:24:41.724
Thank you so much for a fantastic presentation, Sam.

1446
01:24:41.844 --> 01:24:43.864
I have a question about your STING story.

1447
01:24:43.904 --> 01:24:44.044
So

1448
01:24:45.224 --> 01:24:48.304
cancers are not just composed of cancer cells, right?

1449
01:24:48.384 --> 01:24:52.144
There are other immune cells in there, and one of the appeals of the

1450
01:24:52.224 --> 01:24:53.204
STING agonist was that-

1451
01:24:53.244 --> 01:24:53.344
Yeah

1452
01:24:53.354 --> 01:24:57.144
... they're going to stimulate these immune cells, which clearly didn't

1453
01:24:57.224 --> 01:25:00.873
work. So the question is, so what is happening to

1454
01:25:00.944 --> 01:25:03.484
these immune cells, like antigen-presenting cells?

1455
01:25:03.584 --> 01:25:03.594
I

1456
01:25:04.824 --> 01:25:08.714
guess, is the chronic cGAS stimulation cancer cells also inducing

1457
01:25:08.764 --> 01:25:12.504
